OL,3,CThe economy is turning a corner - but
OL,4,Cvery slowly
OL,6,FThe latest figures showing the economy
OL,7,Fnot growing at all in April will not
OL,8,Fhave been welcome news to political
OL,9,Fparties, ITV News Economics Editor
OL,10,FJoel Hills reports.
OL,12,FEconomic growth stalled in the rain in
OL,13,FApril.
OL,15,FThe headline is terrible news for
OL,16,FRishi Sunak in the middle of an
OL,17,Felection campaign, but then the
OL,18,Fheadline doesn't tell the whole story.
