OL,3,CThe economy is turning a corner - but
OL,4,Cvery slowly
OL,6,FGrowth in the three months between
OL,7,FFebruary and April was up 0.7% on the
OL,8,Fprevious three months and there is
OL,9,Fplenty of evidence to support Sunak's
OL,10,Fclaim that a corner has been turned.
OL,12,FInflation has receded. Pay has been
OL,13,Frising faster than prices for eleven
OL,14,Fmonths and interest rates are forecast
OL,15,Fto start edging down in the months
OL,16,Fahead.
OL,18,FThere's every reason to be hopeful
OL,19,Fthat the worst is now behind us.
