OL,3,CThe economy is turning a corner - but
OL,4,Cvery slowly
OL,6,FAll of the parties in this election
OL,7,Fare promising to grow the economy. All
OL,8,Fof them promise better jobs, better
OL,9,Fpay and higher living standards.
OL,11,FThese are highly desirable aims, but
OL,12,Fthe question we should be asking is
OL,13,Fwhich party has a convincing plan to
OL,14,Fdeliver them?
OL,16,FWhich party has the policies that are
OL,17,Flikely to increase business investment
OL,18,F(which has been lethargic since
OL,19,FBrexit), public investment,
OL,20,Fproductivity and economic growth?
